//-----------------------------------  br tag ----------------------------------------

- It is used to print statements on next line

//------------------------------ attribute : target="_blank" ---------------------------

- It is used to open link in new tab.

//----------------------------- <a href="--" target="_blank">Click Here </a> ----------------------------

------------------------------- Types of stylesheets: ------------------------------------------------

1. Internal - inside html file itself (inside style tag) ---- in the head tag
			<style>
            	.link{
                	color :blueviolet;
            	}
        	</style>

2. External - inside different css file
				<link rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' href='style.css'>
				
3. Inline - with the element itself
			<p class ='intro' style="color:blueviolet;">
			

------------------------------------ Common properties ---------------------------------------------

	1.content
	2.padding
	3.border
	4.Margin
	
----------------------------------  Border width sequence( Top Right Bottom Left ) ------------------------------------------


--------------------------------------- div ----------------------------------------------------

- It is used to  create space for contents (box model )
- Systematic


---------------------------------------- float -----------------------------------------------

it is used to float the content to the right or left in the box(div space)


----------------------------- <img src="--" id ="image">------------------------------------------------


------------------ css property :- overflow=auto ---------------------------------------------------------

-If the content does not fits , then scrollbar is added
























	
			

